276
00:36:34.150 -> 00:36:35.520
Maestru!

277
00:36:36.020 -> 00:36:38.480
Nu ti-ai atins mancarea!

278
00:36:39.650 -> 00:36:41.070
Nu-ti place?

279
00:36:41.240 -> 00:36:43.570
Nu. nu-i asa.

280
00:36:44.990 -> 00:36:46.950
De cand a venit Banki-ul ...

281
00:36:47.030 -> 00:36:50.830
hanurile din Bito
s-au irosit.

