289
00:37:37.330 -> 00:37:38.670
O multime!

290
00:37:42.050 -> 00:37:43.630
Unde este toaleta?

291
00:37:44.090 -> 00:37:45.970
Pe hol.

292
00:38:06.700 -> 00:38:08.740
