304
00:39:07.670 -> 00:39:08.970
Perfect!

305
00:39:09.470 -> 00:39:10.840
Tata!

306
00:39:11.840 -> 00:39:13.800
Acesta este Squire Fujihira.

307
00:39:22.150 -> 00:39:25.480
Este foarte departe de a fi nimeni.

308
00:39:28.690 -> 00:39:30.070
Mizam pe tine.

309
00:39:41.170 -> 00:39:43.170
Pot vorbi cu tine?

310
00:39:56.180 -> 00:39:59.310
Banki nu este
seful tau de razboi obisnuit.

311
00:40:00.390 -> 00:40:03.190
Era un samurai
de nume bun ...

312
00:40:03.980 -> 00:40:10.030
recomandat Shogunului
ca instructor de scrima.

313
00:40:12.950 -> 00:40:14.990
Deci ce l-a facut bandit?

314
00:40:17.030 -> 00:40:19.580
Fata ii era arsa.

315
00:40:20.200 -> 00:40:22.910
El este desfigurat oribil.

316
00:40:25.080 -> 00:40:28.170
Aspectul lui
a fost atat de hidos. spun ei ...

317
00:40:29.630 -> 00:40:33.010
ca a fost condus
din postul sau oficial.

318
00:40:35.260 -> 00:40:36.640
Pentru aspectul lui?

319
00:40:38.350 -> 00:40:39.970
Banki-to ...

320
00:40:41.100 -> 00:40:45.980
