328
00:41:41.540 -> 00:41:43.330
Chiar tipul. nu?

329
00:41:44.620 -> 00:41:46.830
Un tata asa ...

330
00:41:48.420 -> 00:41:51.920
te face sa vrei
sa-ti blazesti urmele.

331
00:42:21.030 -> 00:42:25.370
Mi-a spus seful Chobei
despre acest loc secret.

332
00:42:26.040 -> 00:42:28.580
