333
00:42:29.120 -> 00:42:32.170
Astepti aici. O sa-l iau.

334
00:42:34.210 -> 00:42:35.340
Coma!

335
00:42:48.810 -> 00:42:50.980
Kotaro ti se pare dragut.

336
00:42:52.060 -> 00:42:53.820
Iti plac copii?

337
00:42:55.690 -> 00:42:57.110
ii urasc.

338
00:42:59.240 -> 00:43:00 740
Sunt daunatori.

339
00:43:03.200 -> 00:43:04.660
Nu se vor opri.

340
00:43:10.670 -> 00:43:18.090
Dar sunt curate de inima
ca sa poti avea incredere in ele.

341
00:43:24.050 -> 00:43:26.140
Dar nu adultii ...

342
00:43:28.390 -> 00:43:29.930
Nu majoritatea.

343
00:43:34.150 -> 00:43:35.570
Ai o muscatura.

344
00:43:40.610 -> 00:43:41.950
Nu. nu ...

345
00:43:52.250 -> 00:43:54.380
Hei. da!

346
00:44:05.720 -> 00:44:07.350
Bine bine bine!

347
00:44:27.990 -> 00:44:33.540
- Din nou diseara. dorm singura ...

348
00:44:35.290 -> 00:44:40.340
„Imaginati-va sa fiu balansat
pe genunchiul mamei mele.

349
00:44:44.130 -> 00:44:45.930
Melodia aia cantata ...

350
00:44:47.470 -> 00:44:49.180
Cum merge?

351
00:44:54.060 -> 00:44:55.730
'Abandonat...

352
00:44:58.320 -> 00:45:00 730
imi imaginez chipul
Nu am vazut niciodata...

353
00:45:02.530 -> 00:45:04.400
