357
00:45:25.180 -> 00:45:26.840
Poate intr-o zi.

358
00:45:44.190 -> 00:45:46.990
Vei ramane o vreme?

359
00:45:49.370 -> 00:45:51.240
Pana la finalizarea cautarii mele.

360
00:45:53.790 -> 00:45:55.250
Vad...

361
00:46:06.880 -> 00:46:12.010
S-ar putea sa existe o lupta intre
Shirakawa si Banki-to.

362
00:46:15.810 -> 00:46:17.730
Intentionati sa luptati?

363
00:46:23.030 -> 00:46:25.900
Ei bine. servesc Shirakawa ...

364
00:46:30.030 -> 00:46:31.410
Stai in afara ei.

365
00:46:37.120 -> 00:46:41.210
Lipind nasul in lucruri
doar aduce probleme.

366
00:46:45.670 -> 00:46:49.470
Nu pot sa stau doar
in timp ce tovarasii mei sunt ucisi.

367
00:46:55.890 -> 00:47:00.270
Ai fi putut ajuta aceasta fata
bateau.

368
00:47:09.110 -> 00:47:10.360
De ce este ...

369
00:47:11.780 -> 00:47:14.160
