370
00:47:19.960 -> 00:47:26.420
Cand esti orb.
nu poti vedea granita.

371
00:47:29.260 -> 00:47:31.510
Zi sau noapte...

372
00:47:32.300 -> 00:47:35.100
Sau daca drumul se termina brusc ...

373
00:47:35.890 -> 00:47:37.850
Nu vedeti linia intre ele.

374
00:47:39.390 -> 00:47:41.480
Totul te sperie.

375
00:47:42.980 -> 00:47:47.980
Daca un barbat e bun sau rau ...
cum pot vedea sa stiu?

376
00:47:48.990 -> 00:47:51.070
Nu pot spune nicio diferenta.

377
00:47:51.990 -> 00:47:54.490
Nici nu pot vedea ...

378
00:47:54.780 -> 00:47:56.700
daca sunt viu sau mort!

379
00:48:06.960 -> 00:48:12.760
Nu ca chiar imi pasa
daca traiesc. oricum.

380
00:48:31.820 -> 00:48:32.900
Astepta!

381
00:48:39.160 -> 00:48:41.000
Lupta-ma cu asta.

382
00:48:43.500 -> 00:48:45.210
