384
00:49:14.740 -> 00:49:15.910
Iata.

385
00:50:05.960 -> 00:50:07.920
Chiar in program!

386
00:50:08.710 -> 00:50:11.420
Magistratul va fi multumit.

387
00:50:12.920 -> 00:50:14.010
Poate.

388
00:50:14.510 -> 00:50:16.510
Banki-to ar trebui sa taca ...

389
00:50:17.050 -> 00:50:20.590
in timp ce Magistratul este in jur.

390
00:50:34.280 -> 00:50:38.240
Imi pare rau.
N-am vrut sa te lovesc atat de tare.

391
00:50:40.620 -> 00:50:41.740
Doare?

392
00:50:44.750 -> 00:50:47.330
Deci esti mai bun decat ea ...

393
00:50:48.830 -> 00:50:52.590
Da. Sunt foarte bun.

394
00:50:55.760 -> 00:50:57.920
Dar numai cu o sabie de lemn.

395
00:51:00.590 -> 00:51:03.100
Nu pot sa lovesc cu unul real.

396
00:51:05.060 -> 00:51:06.350
De ce nu?

397
00:51:13.980 -> 00:51:15.110
Tatal meu...

398
00:51:16.280 -> 00:51:19.320
<i> a predat arte martiale
pentru clanul Odaka. </i>

399
00:51:41.760 -> 00:51:43.010
Toma!

400
00:51:47.220 -> 00:51:48.770
Mama!

401
00:51:52.940 -> 00:51:55.270
Mama nu a fost ucisa ...

402
00:51:58.150 -> 00:52:00.070
dar era orbita.

403
00:52:07.450 -> 00:52:12.080
si nu am fost niciodata in stare
sa traga din nou o sabie.

404
00:52:14.330 -> 00:52:18.500
Nimeni nu m-a batut vreodata
cu o sabie de lemn.

405
00:52:20.880 -> 00:52:24.930
Dar ca fiu al unui maestru de sabie
cine nu putea sa traga o sabie adevarata ...

406
00:52:25.350 -> 00:52:26.930
Mi-am rusinat casa.

407
00:52:28.970 -> 00:52:31.430
Tatal meu a inceput sa ma urasca.

408
00:52:35.230 -> 00:52:39.570
Cinci ani in urma.
el si-a adoptat cel mai bun student

409
00:52:40.860 -> 00:52:42.900
ca mostenitor in locul meu.

410
00:52:47.370 -> 00:52:49.740
si am plecat intr-un pelerinaj ...

411
00:52:53.710 -> 00:52:56.250
de care tot incerc
pentru a gasi sfarsitul.

412
00:53:00.380 -> 00:53:03.420
Dar mama mea
nu m-a parasit niciodata.

413
00:53:05.220 -> 00:53:09.310
<i> M-a incurajat mereu
pentru a deveni un adevarat samurai. </i>

414
00:53:11.980 -> 00:53:16.020
<i> Dar cand aveam 15 ani. ea a murit. </i>

415
00:53:18.940 -> 00:53:23.780
<i> Chiar si cand era grav bolnava.
ea a luptat pentru viata. </i>

416
00:53:26.570 -> 00:53:31.120
<i> Desi era orb.
nu a renuntat niciodata la speranta. </i>

417
00:53:33.330 -> 00:53:36.960
Voia cu disperare sa traiasca ...

418
00:53:40.960 -> 00:53:42.880
dar asta nu trebuia sa fie.

419
00:54:02.820 -> 00:54:04.150
Eu sunt...

420
00:54:06.030 -> 00:54:07.450
cine sunt.

421
00:55:43.790 -> 00:55:46.210
Magistratul a sosit!

422
00:57:20.930 -> 00:57:22.520
Deci nu este ...

423
00:57:23.140 -> 00:57:26.100
omul pe care il cauti.

424
00:58:09.900 -> 00:58:11.520
Pleci?

425
00:59:22.050 -> 00:59:23.140
Yasuke!

426
00:59:47.750 -> 00:59:48.790
Yasuke!

427
00:59:49.750 -> 00:59:53.670
Nu-mi pasa daca esti
un magistrat sau nu!

428
00:59:53.790 -> 00:59:55460
Vei regreta asta!

429
00:59:57.380 -> 00:59:58.710
Maestru!

430
01:00:02.510 -> 01:00:04.970
Esti Toma Fujihira?

431
01:00:07.220 -> 01:00:09.140
Omoara-i!

432
01:00:33.880 -> 01:00:35.130
Ce s-a intamplat?!

433
01:00:37.460 -> 01:00:38.670
Milord!

434
01:00:45.930 -> 01:00:47.140
Acum asculta...

435
01:00:48.180 -> 01:00:50.810
N-ai vazut nimic.

436
01:00:53.730 -> 01:00:58.480
Totul este calm in Bito.
Este un oras pasnic.

437
01:01:00.320 -> 01:01:03.400
Bito este un oras minunat!

438
01:01:04.360 -> 01:01:09.080
Daca doriti sa va mentineti pozitia.
nu spune nimic despre noi.

439
01:01:12.500 -> 01:01:13.960
Jur!

440
01:01:22.920 -> 01:01:27.050
Ceva bodyguard ai. Toraji.

441
01:01:28.050 -> 01:01:33.640
Doar nu te deranja. ca la batranul tau.
Vei trai mai mult.

442
01:01:34.390 -> 01:01:35.520
Taci!

443
01:01:58.670 -> 01:01:59.960
Salvati...

444
01:02:03.800 -> 01:02:05.260
Salvati...

445
01:02:08.140 -> 01:02:09.300
orasul!

446
01:02:10.050 -> 01:02:11.100
Tata!

447
01:02:11.600 -> 01:02:12.970
Hei!

448
01:02:13.270 -> 01:02:15.640
Tata!

449
01:02:16.140 -> 01:02:17.350
Tata!

450
01:02:18.940 -> 01:02:20.650
Aceasta a fost o greseala...

451
01:02:21.690 -> 01:02:23.150
Astepta!

452
01:02:24.070 -> 01:02:27.070
Avem nevoie de Shirakawas
tinut in viata.

453
01:02:27.820 -> 01:02:29.660
Am facut destul.

454
01:02:31.740 -> 01:02:33.370
Mergeau!

455
01:02:39.420 -> 01:02:44.210
Unde este acea singura poza
seful vorbea?

456
01:02:44.670 -> 01:02:47.800
Adu-l pe acest tip cu noi.

457
01:02:48.090 -> 01:02:49.470
Nu este el.

458
01:02:56.270 -> 01:02:58.690
Du-ma la Banki.

459
01:03:12.580 -> 01:03:15.740
Banki cunoaste un barbat
care lupta in stilul meu.

460
01:03:22.670 -> 01:03:24.040
Interesant...

461
01:04:17.180 -> 01:04:18.390
In regula!

462
01:05:43.850 -> 01:05:45.230
Şef!

463
01:05:45.900 -> 01:05:50.570
Nu era Toma Fujihira
care i-a taiat pe oamenii nostri.

464
01:06:00.450 -> 01:06:04.500
Ce ne spuneti
a fost femeia aceea?

465
01:06:12.050 -> 01:06:14.130
Asta e prostie!

466
01:06:15.930 -> 01:06:17.930
Convinge-te singur.

467
01:07:07.980 -> 01:07:09.520
Sunteti Banki?

468
01:07:25.370 -> 01:07:27.620
Nu sunt destul de bun?

469
01:08:08.000 -> 01:08:09.250
O omor!

470
01:09:26.950 -> 01:09:29.620
Sunteti fara speranta!

471
01:09:40.670 -> 01:09:42.630
Esti aici pentru mine?

472
01:09:43.920 -> 01:09:46.010
Vreau sa intreb ceva.

473
01:09:55.140 -> 01:09:56.940
Sunt bine. stii.

474
01:09:58.310 -> 01:09:59.940
Taci!

475
01:10:01.980 -> 01:10:03.820
Nu faceti zgomot.

476
01:10:10.660 -> 01:10:13.620
Am vazut un barbat
care lupta ca tine.

477
01:10:23.170 -> 01:10:25.880
Era orb. dar foarte bun.

478
01:11:51.430 -> 01:11:53.590
