488
01:12:57.280 -> 01:13:00.160
A batut-o! L-am vazut!

489
01:13:11.340 -> 01:13:13.670
Vom incheia Banki-to.

490
01:13:15.840 -> 01:13:17.640
Nu mai fugi.

491
01:13:21.230 -> 01:13:24.060
Am pierdut o multime de barbati.

492
01:13:27.110 -> 01:13:30.400
Avem nevoie de toti oamenii pe care ii putem obtine!

493
01:13:36.030 -> 01:13:38.070
'Mare maestru'...

494
01:13:40.410 -> 01:13:45.210
Daca intr-adevar esti atat de bun.
atunci il omori pe Banki pentru noi.

495
01:13:58.050 -> 01:13:59.680
Inainte de asta...

496
01:14:05.230 -> 01:14:06.810
Exista un lucru ...

497
01:14:08.650 -> 01:14:10.730
Eu trebuie sa fac.

498
01:14:47.900 -> 01:14:49.600
Te doare?

499
01:14:54.070 -> 01:14:59.280
Ce a fost pentru tine orbul?

500
01:15:04.120 -> 01:15:09.790
El si cu mine.
amandoi am mirosit ca niste persoane din afara.

501
01:15:13.050 -> 01:15:18.220
si tu faci.

502
01:15:22.800 -> 01:15:24.350
Suntem la fel.

503
01:15:25.970 -> 01:15:28.350
Suntem tratati ca niste fiare.

504
01:15:34.110 -> 01:15:36.530
Ne dau cu piciorul ...

505
01:15:38.570 -> 01:15:41.110
si ne lasa sa murim pe campuri.

506
01:15:44.620 -> 01:15:46.200
intinde-te acolo...

507
01:15:48.750 -> 01:15:50.960
atata timp cat doriti.

508
01:15:54.090 -> 01:16:00.550
si atunci voi lua
foarte buna grija de tine.

509
01:20:22.690 -> 01:20:27.270
<i> Spuneti missusului
Nu am facut niciodata nimic. </i>

510
01:20:29.280 -> 01:20:31.950
<i> Nu am alt loc. </i>

511
01:20:33.660 -> 01:20:35.200
<i> Vreau sa ma intorc. </i>

512
01:23:02.260 -> 01:23:03.430
Ichi!

513
01:23:04.640 -> 01:23:06.230
Te salvez!

514
01:23:14.530 -> 01:23:17.110
Unde e femeia ?!

515
01:23:17.240 -> 01:23:18.400
Gaseste-o!

516
01:23:18.530 -> 01:23:19.860
Dupa ea!

517
01:23:21.120 -> 01:23:22.160
Kihachi!

518
01:23:25.250 -> 01:23:26.450
in felul acesta!

519
01:24:06.700 -> 01:24:07.950
Cine esti tu?!

520
01:24:11.170 -> 01:24:12.460
Toma Fujihira!

521
01:24:15.340 -> 01:24:17.340
Femeia aia e a mea.

522
01:25:42.630 -> 01:25:44.220
Trebuie sa te odihnesti.

523
01:25:52.560 -> 01:25:54.060
Omul...

524
01:25:56.560 -> 01:25:58.150
Era mort.

525
01:26:05.700 -> 01:26:07.110
Tatal tau?

526
01:26:17.130 -> 01:26:19.630
M-a lasat cu trupa de gasca.

527
01:26:21.960 -> 01:26:27.470
Se intorcea uneori
si invata-ma sa lupt.

528
01:26:32.180 -> 01:26:34.560
Acum nu pot afla niciodata adevarul.

529
01:26:40.190 -> 01:26:47.070
Trupa m-a alungat.
N-am vrut sa-l omor pe barbat.

530
01:26:49.910 -> 01:26:51.950
Eram complet derutat.

531
01:26:54.950 -> 01:26:57.540
Nu simt nimic.

532
01:27:03.590 -> 01:27:05.880
Mai bine muream.

533
01:27:08.640 -> 01:27:11.010
Dar voiam sa-l cunosc
inainte de a muri...

534
01:27:12.140 -> 01:27:15.060
si intreaba daca a fost tatal meu ...

535
01:27:23.360 -> 01:27:25.150
Nu trebuie sa mori.

536
01:27:32.620 -> 01:27:34.280
Nu trebuie sa mori!

537
01:28:57.580 -> 01:28:58.990
In regula!

538
01:28:59.330 -> 01:29:02.910
Sunt mai multi.
dar tot putem castiga!

539
01:29:04.130 -> 01:29:09.420
Au mai mult de doua ori
deci omorati cel putin doi inainte de a cadea.

540
01:29:11.800 -> 01:29:12.920
Genta!

541
01:29:14.890 -> 01:29:17.010
Intra in apropiere si lupta-te!

542
01:29:17.970 -> 01:29:19.680
Da-mi unul!

543
01:29:30.360 -> 01:29:31.780
Maestru...

544
01:29:33.200 -> 01:29:35.030
Nu fugi pe noi de data asta.

545
01:29:36.530 -> 01:29:37.950
Ei vin!

546
01:29:38.080 -> 01:29:39.990
Multi!

547
01:29:43.120 -> 01:29:44.580
Dreapta!

548
01:30:59.200 -> 01:31:02.280
Eu sunt Toraji
din familia Shirakawa!

549
01:31:03.950 -> 01:31:05.500
Banki!

550
01:31:07.040 -> 01:31:10.170
Astazi ne stabilim o data pentru totdeauna!

551
01:31:11.960 -> 01:31:15.510
Acest loc ne mai este de folos.

552
01:31:17.760 -> 01:31:19.010
Toraji!

553
01:31:20.300 -> 01:31:21.550
Ma tem...

554
01:31:22.760 -> 01:31:25.810
te vei alatura tatalui tau.

555
01:31:28.060 -> 01:31:32.650
in ziua de azi. tu si acest loc
sunt terminate.

556
01:33:07.370 -> 01:33:09.240
Ichi. esti treaz?

557
01:33:15.790 -> 01:33:17.130
Unde e Toma?

558
01:33:22.550 -> 01:33:24.130
Ce s-a intamplat?

559
01:35:53.160 -> 01:35:55.490
Aceasta este pentru tatal meu!

560
01:37:31.130 -> 01:37:33.050
Toma Fujihira!

561
01:37:37.140 -> 01:37:38.720
infrunta-ma.

562
01:37:43.020 -> 01:37:45.480
Da-i femeia inapoi.

563
01:37:52.150 -> 01:37:53.990
Unde este el?

564
01:37:58.910 -> 01:38:01.080
A alergat din nou?

565
01:38:10.130 -> 01:38:13.630
Cred ca va trebui sa plec.

566
01:38:44.200 -> 01:38:46.000
Du-l ucide!

567
01:39:12.110 -> 01:39:14.400
Femeia aia e a mea.

568
01:39:22.740 -> 01:39:23.990
Ichi ...

569
01:39:27.080 -> 01:39:29.000
Nu voi da drumul niciodata.

570
01:40:39.360 -> 01:40:41.820
Omoara-l...

571
01:40:45.240 -> 01:40:47.490
Maestru.

572
01:41:09.640 -> 01:41:10.890
Toma!

573
01:42:55.790 -> 01:42:56.870
Coma!

574
01:44:25.880 -> 01:44:27.510
Cum e Banki?

575
01:44:43.150 -> 01:44:44.650
A murit.

576
01:44:49.610 -> 01:44:51.030
Banki este ...

577
01:44:52.740 -> 01:44:54.160
mort.

578
01:45:16.010 -> 01:45:17.600
Trai!

579
01:45:20.890 -> 01:45:22.140
Ichi!

580
01:45:26.400 -> 01:45:27.980
Trebuie sa traiesti!

581
01:47:26.890 -> 01:47:29.020
Granita nu am putut sa o vad ...

582
01:47:32.150 -> 01:47:34.110
incet devine clar.

583
01:47:45.080 -> 01:47:47.580
Unul care a cazut ...

584
01:47:50.170 -> 01:47:53.630
nu se mai poate ridica niciodata.

585
01:48:05.060 -> 01:48:08.930
Mai ales unul
care se afla in sange.

586
01:48:23.830 -> 01:48:26.370
Nu te voi ierta niciodata.

587
01:48:46.600 -> 01:48:49.180
Nu ma poti infrange niciodata!

588
01:50:24.070 -> 01:50:25.360
Mare sef!

589
01:51:29.260 -> 01:51:32.050
Unde vei merge acum?

590
01:51:33.310 -> 01:51:34.810
Spre Odaka.

591
01:51:36.980 -> 01:51:38.230
Orasul natal al lui Toma?

592
01:51:41.770 -> 01:51:45.190
Sa-si puna sabia
pe mormantul mamei sale.

593
01:53:05.980 -> 01:53:10.940
Se pare ca am nevoie de lumina
pentru a merge cu. pana la urma.

594
01:53:16.620 -> 01:53:21.290
Cu aceasta lumina. ma simt
in sfarsit imi pot vedea putin calea.

595
01:54:09.960 -> 01:54:11.090
Ne vom intalni din nou!

596
01:55:11.090 -> 01:55:13.090
Esir
